t get the best of you or snag you low on HPs or lagged.<br><br>Are you basically vulnerable until you get uber ToV or planar gear?<br><br>Thanks for the nfo <p><center>-----------------------------------------<br>Baron Arkaan Riftwalker<br>56 Evoker<br>Bristlebane</center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarkaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arkaan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 12/26/01 8:46:14 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarkaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arkaan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/27/01 7:01:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://arkaan.dhs.org:88/eq/arksig.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for 50-60 RZ wizards</span><hr size=1> no RZ wizzies? <p><center>-----------------------------------------<br>Baron Arkaan Riftwalker<br>56 Evoker<br>Bristlebane</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaueadillc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AueadillC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/28/01 1:35:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for 50-60 RZ wizards</span><hr size=1> Im a VZ wizard which is very similar to RZ and with resist gear on and self buffed im averaging 