 PVPing in full gear and having all the extra mana, I've looted fungi tunics, about 3 full sets of BD jewelry, enough crap to fully gear my twink ROG, etc.<br><br>Bottom line:  Even though there's item loot, you need to play smart and wear your best gear at all times.  The people that don't do that are the people that get regularly die.  (You know who you are.  Lol.)<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uavih8r.showPublicProfile?language=EN>avih8r</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/29/01 9:36:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> err.</span><hr size=1> &quot;..get regularly KILLED.&quot;  is what I meant to say.  Damn this message board and it's lack of editing features.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarkaan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arkaan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/30/01 11:11:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://arkaan.dhs.org:88/eq/arksig.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question for 50-60 RZ wizards</span><hr size=1> Great thanks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><center>-----------------------------------------<br>Baron Arkaan Riftwalker<br